title: The Freddie and Paul Show Episode 68
description:
Here we announce the creation of Freddie's new channel. Here is a link to the first video on the new channel. Take a look and subscribe. https://youtu.be/rN2LZ0KEu8k 

The Freddie and Paul show will continue but the new channel will give Freddie more time to do what he wants with his music. The Freddie and Paul show will retain it's talk format.

Freddie's own channel is found at https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCWg_7efiSKUYR4cVexI-TfQ
